- Sure.

242
00:15:05,960 --> 00:15:08,010
Gribbet. Gribbet.

243
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:09,178
Gribbet.

244
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:13,710
Yeah. All-natural,
no dyes is a good business.

245
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:15,710
All-natural children's toys.

246
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:18,650
Toy companies. They don't
arbitrarily mark up their frogs.

247
00:15:18,660 --> 00:15:21,690
They don't lie about how much they
spend on research and development.

248
00:15:22,140 --> 00:15:26,760
The worst that a toy company could be
accused of is making a really boring frog.

249
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,406
Gribbet, gribbet, gribbet.

250
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:31,659
You know another
really good business?

251
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:35,329
Teeny, tiny baby coffins.

252
00:15:36,900 --> 00:15:38,610
You can get 'em in frog green,

253
00:15:38,610 --> 00:15:40,720
fire-engine red, really.

254
00:15:41,752 --> 00:15:45,730
The antibodies in yummy mummy
only protect the kid for six months,

255
00:15:45,730 --> 00:15:48,425
which is why these companies
think they can gouge you.

256
00:15:48,490 --> 00:15:51,595
They think that you'll spend whatever
they ask to keep your kid alive.

257
00:15:51,990 --> 00:15:53,931
Want to change things?
Prove 'em wrong.

258
00:15:54,100 --> 00:15:55,910
Few hundred parents like you
decide they'd rather

259
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:58,700
let their kid die than cough up
40 bucks for a vaccination,

260
00:15:58,710 --> 00:16:01,397
believe me,
prices will drop really fast.

261
00:16:02,064 --> 00:16:04,260
Gribbet, gribbet, gribbet,
gribbet, gribbet.

262
00:16:04,441 --> 00:16:04,942
Gribbet.

263
00:16:06,652 --> 00:16:07,945
Tell me what she has.

264
00:16:10,980 --> 00:16:11,824
