00:40:06,880 --> 00:40:10,678
Looked it up on the Internet.
It's one of those trait things.

684
00:40:10,740 --> 00:40:12,972
That's right. It's autosomal dominant.

685
00:40:14,223 --> 00:40:16,016
Since neither of your
parents have cleft chins,

686
00:40:16,016 --> 00:40:18,519
it's highly unlikely you're
biologically related.

687
00:40:21,021 --> 00:40:24,733
- Are you sure you're okay?
- I've got no problems with being adopted.

688
00:40:26,569 --> 00:40:27,820
I love my parents.

689
00:40:31,140 --> 00:40:33,120
- How's he doing?
- He's doing pretty well.

690
00:40:33,784 --> 00:40:34,785
He's a smart kid.

691
00:40:35,786 --> 00:40:37,246
I think he's gonna be fine.

692
00:40:41,292 --> 00:40:43,350
- Hey.
- Thanks.

693
00:41:19,163 --> 00:41:20,789
Wheels, 18. Wheels.

